---
import Block from "./../../atoms/block/index.astro";
import SectionHead from "./../../molecules/section-head/index.astro";
import Paragraph from "./../../atoms/paragraph/index.astro";
import Highlight from "./../../atoms/highlight/index.astro";
---

<Block padding="50px 0">
  <SectionHead prefix="My" title=" Story" />
  <Block padding="20px 0 0 0">
    <Paragraph
      ><i><Highlight>Lead Frontend Developer</Highlight></i> with a <i
        >Fullstack</i
      >
      background. Deep knowledge of libraries related to the <i
        ><Highlight>React</Highlight></i
      > ecosystem including cross platform development. Clean code and tdd fan. I'm
      a team player and I can work in teams with Scrum and Kanban methodology.</Paragraph
    >
  </Block>
  <Block padding="20px 0 0 0">
    <Paragraph
      >I'm hungry for the latest technical innovations, but I'm also inclined to
      choose the right solution for the purpose rather than the latest one.</Paragraph
    >
  </Block>
  <Block padding="20px 0 0 0">
    <Paragraph
      >I'm a very kind person and I have great listening skills. I'm a <i
        ><Highlight>proactive</Highlight></i
      >
      person and I believe that every voice has its importance and every team member
      is fundamental, but I'm also able to make solid decisions when necessary and
      take full responsibility for them.</Paragraph
    >
  </Block>
</Block>
